        <TD bgcolor='black' valign='top'><font color='white' face='Verdana' size='2'> I have found mine to be REAL handy in Firepot traveling.</P><P>&lt;a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=87902"&gt;Tumlan SoulStalker&lt;/href&gt;</font></td>
